Closing the gap: increases in life expectancy among treated HIV-positive 
individuals in the United States and Canada.

Samji H(1), Cescon A(1), Hogg RS(2), Modur SP(3), Althoff KN(3), Buchacz K(4), 
Burchell AN(5), Cohen M(6), Gebo KA(3), Gill MJ(7), Justice A(8), Kirk G(3), 
